 * pino/sentry/OTel via custom RequestHooks.
 *
 * @example
 * \`\`\`
 * new ODataV3Client({ ..., hooks: consoleHook({ logBodies: true }) })
 * // stderr:
 * // [1c-odata] → GET /Catalog_X?$top=10
 * // [1c-odata] ← 200 127ms 5.3KB
